# Upload and approval

## Upload file and approve documents

```shell
curl -X POST "<%= config[:url] %>/v1/financial_institutions/credit_lines" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ${secret_key}" -H "X-API-KEY: ${api_key}" \
  -F "file=@/path/to/your/file.txt" \
